data.description: HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER LOCATION IN SPRING! This gem's situated in Northwood Pines@Northgate Xing a block from ExxonMobil campus & City Pl Plaza.The Woodlands mall 2 exits North, minutes from schools, restaurants & shopping.Easy access to Grand Pkwy, Hardy Toll Rd & I-45.Walk along Spring Creek Nature Trail or in the neighborhood park, splash pad & lake.Home nestled in a cul-de-sac & backs up to a private wooded area.Floorplan offers overszd bedrms, walk in closets, 9’ ceilings, two-car garage & covered front porch & back patio.Upgrades include: fresh paint inside/out, new window coverings, ceiling fans, updated baths, kitchen w/custom built pantry & laundry room, granite countertops, new door hardware. Large built in entertainment center in living area.Exterior upgrades: leaded glass entry door, pavers on side yard, new fence & roof. Water heater, air-conditioning condenser & garage door were replaced in the last 5 years. Schedule your showing before it’s gone! Survey@Buyer's expense.
